      "rationale": "Validation was performed on the FDA generic centrifugal pump, which is geometrically representative of the CPB device class. Operating conditions span the clinical CPB range. The validation scenario is judged sufficiently similar to the COU to support MRL 2 credibility without full COU-device-specific validation."
