    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required gradation levels for MRL 2. The six non-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out per ASME V&V 40 MRL 2 requirements. The CFD model is judged credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. The relative hemolysis index predictions are within the 15% acceptance band across all five operating points, and the RH < 1 criterion is satisfied for the candidate device relative to the predicate. The credibility assessment supports regulatory submission.",
